import React, { Component } from 'react'
import Tabs from 'shared/tabs'
import HistoryBehavior from './components/history'

const { TabList, Tab, TabPanels, TabPanel } = Tabs

export default class Behaviors extends Component {
  render () {
    return (
      <Tabs>
        <TabList isToggle>
          <Tab>Ingresos</Tab>
          <Tab>Gastos</Tab>
        </TabList>
        <TabPanels>
          <TabPanel>
            <HistoryBehavior key='incomes' type='incomes' />
          </TabPanel>
          <TabPanel>
            <HistoryBehavior key='expenses' type='expenses' />
          </TabPanel>
        </TabPanels>
      </Tabs>
    )
  }
}
